WEBVTT

00:00.127 --> 00:02.108
Previously on "Once Upon a Time"...

00:02.188 --> 00:02.997
What do you want?

00:03.003 --> 00:05.041
Sorry to commandeer
your vessel, Captain,

00:05.047 --> 00:06.614
but I'm afraid for what I have planned,

00:06.682 --> 00:08.449
you can't be in Storybrooke.

00:08.551 --> 00:09.617
Emma, are you there?

00:09.719 --> 00:12.453
Gideon... he sent me away.

00:12.555 --> 00:14.555
I would never leave you.

00:14.624 --> 00:15.956
What the hell do I have to do?

00:16.058 --> 00:17.691
Kill the Black Fairy.

00:17.793 --> 00:19.026
Did she harm you?

00:19.128 --> 00:20.628
She toughened me up.

00:20.730 --> 00:22.930
What did she do to you?

00:22.999 --> 00:24.498
Depends what you mean.

